data.description: Recent repairs made and back on the market! Let the previous buyer's loss be your gain! Tucked away at the end of a quiet dead end street, this adorable four bedroom home is just what you've been looking for! From the moment you walk through the door you'll appreciate countless updates throughout, from the modern shiplap fireplace to the eat-in kitchen with granite countertops and stainless appliances. In addition to three bedrooms and a full bathroom upstairs, another large bonus-room and second full-bathroom on the first floor makes a perfect theater room as it is currently used, or a spacious fourth bedroom! When you're through inside, you've got multiple fabulous outdoor spaces to get out and enjoy the Summer evenings ahead, with a lovely back patio, second floor screened porch, and a fully-fenced back yard! This home checks all of the boxes and will not last long- book your showing today! SELLING AS-IS. Inspection report available per request.
